&lt;/style&gt;

&lt;p&gt;​​The Recurrence. Every 90 years, 12 gods reincarnate on earth for 2 years. In
2014, the gods are living as pop icons. Some are high culture, e.g. Lucifer, and
others are underground, e.g. The Morrígan.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Stories of Your Life and Others</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/fiction/chiang-stories-of-your-life-and-others/</link><pubDate>Mon, 25 Oct 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/fiction/chiang-stories-of-your-life-and-others/</guid><description>&lt;div class="citation" citation-icon-class='fas fa-fw fa-book' cited-by-count='' is-main=''&gt;
